msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-03-17-documentation-strategy.adoc:16
msgid "I'm sure by now you've noticed a few changes in the docs so I'd like to take the opportunity to explain what's been going on."
msgstr ""

